Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦敦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去哪里都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（放学后茶会  前往伦敦！！）
