Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是摇滚～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rock and Roll～
